05:35.117 --> 05:38.250
It would be
my pleasure.

05:38.294 --> 05:39.556
Aww!

05:39.600 --> 05:40.731
Mm.
[ Giggles ]

05:40.775 --> 05:41.993
[ Chuckles ]

05:42.777 --> 05:45.083
I would love it.Thank you.

05:45.127 --> 05:47.825
[ Traditional
Italian music plays]

05:47.869 --> 05:49.044
Mmm!

05:49.087 --> 05:51.568
Pizza, root beer,
empty stage

05:51.612 --> 05:53.614
where the creepy animatronic
gondoliers used to perform.

05:53.657 --> 05:54.832
This is
what it's all about.

05:54.876 --> 05:56.617
We don't need your mom
ormy daughter.

05:56.660 --> 05:58.967
[ Scoffs ] Yeah,we're better off without 'em.

05:59.010 --> 06:00.490
We gota fresh batch of plushies

06:00.534 --> 06:02.100
being loadedto the perfect height.

06:02.144 --> 06:04.189
I better go stop
the plushie stuffer

06:04.233 --> 06:05.408
before he packs them
in too tight.

06:05.452 --> 06:06.757
Hello, good sir.

06:06.801 --> 06:07.976
My name's Louis.

06:08.019 --> 06:10.326
Don't call me "sir."
It feels condescending.

06:10.370 --> 06:11.414
Louis. Sorry.

06:11.458 --> 06:13.068
Um, I was wonderingif you wouldn't mind

06:13.111 --> 06:14.678
not packing the stuffies
too tight.

06:14.722 --> 06:17.638
Listen, I have
very little agency in this job,

06:17.681 --> 06:19.291
except when it comes
to this machine.

06:19.335 --> 06:20.510
I stuff how I want.

06:20.554 --> 06:21.511
Okay.

06:21.555 --> 06:23.470
I totally support youall the way.

06:23.513 --> 06:25.515
It's just,
my friend and I,

06:25.559 --> 06:26.647
we're kind of havinga guys' night.

06:26.690 --> 06:28.431
We're looking forwardto bro-ing out

06:28.475 --> 06:31.347
and clawin' usa stuffed gorilla or two.

06:31.391 --> 06:32.914
Looks like
your bro's busy.

06:32.957 --> 06:34.524
Graham:
Check this out.

06:34.568 --> 06:37.005
Gushers: Oops All Gush.

06:37.048 --> 06:39.007
It's just the juice
from the middle.

06:39.050 --> 06:41.444
Wouldn't the juice
just get everywhere
when you open the packet?

06:41.488 --> 06:43.315
Not if it came
with a straw.

06:43.359 --> 06:45.143
Ah.
Will: Hey, buddy,
machine's free.

06:45.187 --> 06:47.537
You ready to claw'til we can't claw na mah?

06:48.582 --> 06:50.235
I'll handle
this sad stranger.

06:50.279 --> 06:52.890
Do you need help
finding your family, sir?

06:52.934 --> 06:54.022
Are you pretending to...

06:54.065 --> 06:56.241
Oh. Wow.
Okay.

06:56.285 --> 06:57.591
You know what?
[ Chuckles ]

06:57.634 --> 06:59.462
I mistook youfor a friend of mine.

06:59.506 --> 07:00.811
My apologies.

07:00.855 --> 07:03.118
I will be on my way.

07:03.161 --> 07:05.468
