07:09.864 --> 07:12.606
do you think this shade
makes me look too --

07:12.649 --> 07:16.174
Ugh, how do I put this? --
friendly?

07:17.524 --> 07:19.700
You look likea hot cartoon mouse.

07:19.743 --> 07:21.528
Oh. Thank you!

07:21.571 --> 07:23.573
Isn't this fun?

07:23.617 --> 07:27.316
