07:34.628 --> 07:36.325
You don't got to worry
about spicy.

07:36.368 --> 07:37.935
We're reallywalking a line here, huh?

07:37.979 --> 07:39.502
Okay, look,
I just need you

07:39.546 --> 07:41.373
to hang out with Percy
for a couple hours

07:41.417 --> 07:43.941
while I have some alone time
with his dad, alright?

07:43.985 --> 07:45.073
[ Doorbell rings ]

07:45.116 --> 07:47.641
Bright smile,
Sophie!

07:47.684 --> 07:49.338
Good day!

07:49.381 --> 07:51.645
Come in. Come in.

07:51.688 --> 07:53.516
Make yourself
comfortable.

07:53.560 --> 07:55.387
Should we take off
our shoes?

07:55.431 --> 07:58.173
Oh, if you want
to start that way

07:58.216 --> 07:59.870
and see where
the night takes us.

07:59.914 --> 08:02.438
[ Chuckles ]
I'm kidding.

08:02.482 --> 08:04.048
Oh.
[ Chuckles ]

08:06.137 --> 08:07.182
Hi, Percy.

08:07.225 --> 08:09.532
Do you want
to see my...

08:09.576 --> 08:11.665
friend Graham's room?
Sure!

08:11.708 --> 08:12.579
Can we play Orchard?

08:12.622 --> 08:15.233
[ Sighs ]

08:15.277 --> 08:16.452
Maybe.

08:18.367 --> 08:19.411
[ Sighs ]

