Aw.

08:20.456 --> 08:22.414
Where is, uh --
Where is Graham?

08:22.458 --> 08:25.766
Oh, loving life.
[ Chuckles ] Somewhere.

08:25.809 --> 08:26.549
Ah.

08:26.593 --> 08:29.421
Uh, can I, uh,
pour you some wine?

08:29.465 --> 08:30.988
Actually, would you mindif I just ran out

08:31.032 --> 08:32.468
and just took care
of a few errands?

08:32.512 --> 08:33.774
[ Cork pops ]
Heh?

08:33.817 --> 08:34.557
I don't know
about you,

08:34.601 --> 08:37.212
but we go through paper towelslike crazy.

08:37.255 --> 08:39.649
I saw this lady on TVwring one out

08:39.693 --> 08:40.563
and then
just keep using it.

08:40.607 --> 08:41.999
No one really
does that, right?

08:42.043 --> 08:43.914
Yeah. Yeah!
Pbht!

08:43.958 --> 08:45.437
Get out of here.

08:45.481 --> 08:46.700
I already got a man.
[ Chuckles ]

08:46.743 --> 08:47.831
Thanks so much.

08:47.875 --> 08:49.659
Listen, it's, uh --
it's just so nice

08:49.703 --> 08:51.574
to know another single parent
who understands the juggle.

08:51.618 --> 08:52.836
[ Chuckles ]
Yeah.

08:52.880 --> 08:54.838
Anyway, give me a call
if there's a problem.

08:54.882 --> 08:56.274
Actually,
I don't have your cell--

08:56.318 --> 08:58.015
