08:58.059 --> 08:59.147
Fun.

08:59.190 --> 09:02.629
Looks like you're freeto play Orchard with us.

09:02.672 --> 09:03.586
Pbht.

09:06.067 --> 09:07.155
Oops.

09:07.198 --> 09:08.504
You atetoo many apple seeds,

09:08.548 --> 09:10.811
and now you have
arsenic poisoning.

09:10.854 --> 09:12.377
Time to goto the apple hospital.

09:12.421 --> 09:13.596
Again?!

09:13.640 --> 09:15.642
Why do we still have to play
with this creepshow?

09:15.685 --> 09:17.600
I can't go through
another harvest.

09:17.644 --> 09:18.949
You already blew it
with Colin.

09:18.993 --> 09:20.603
I did not.

09:20.647 --> 09:22.431
I just need more time,that's all.

09:22.474 --> 09:23.824
You just watch.

09:23.867 --> 09:24.607
When he gets back,

09:24.651 --> 09:26.740
I'm gonna burn his face offwith my spice.

09:26.783 --> 09:29.264
No more hospital beds.You go rotten.

09:29.307 --> 09:31.179
[ Doorbell rings ]

09:31.222 --> 09:32.441
Hey!

09:32.484 --> 09:34.617
Thanks so much
for watching Percy.

09:34.661 --> 09:35.879
