to find the time

09:42.669 --> 09:43.844
to feed your child

09:43.887 --> 09:45.236
and then go shoppingfor all the food

09:45.280 --> 09:47.108
that is required
for the feeding.

09:47.151 --> 09:48.239
Aah!

09:48.283 --> 09:49.850
They make cat feeders,
why not kid feeders?

09:49.893 --> 09:51.199
[ Chuckles ]
Right?

09:51.242 --> 09:52.635
Right,
we'll be off.
Oh, really?

09:52.679 --> 09:53.854
Already?

09:53.897 --> 09:56.421
But Sophie and Percy
are having so much fun.

09:56.465 --> 09:58.206
Really?
Yeah.

09:58.249 --> 09:59.468
Percy: Apples.

09:59.511 --> 10:01.035
This is huge.

10:01.078 --> 10:02.558
I...

10:02.602 --> 10:05.039
Percy sometimes has troublemaking friends because of the...

10:05.082 --> 10:07.215
breakup.The apple thing? Yeah.

10:07.258 --> 10:08.651
That, um --

10:08.695 --> 10:10.348
But, you know,
if there's one person

10:10.392 --> 10:11.785
that can nerd out
on a single topic,

10:11.828 --> 10:13.656
it is Sophie Cooper.
Okay.

10:13.700 --> 10:16.224
Well, then shall welet this friendship bloom?

10:16.267 --> 10:18.269
Mm-hmm.
I'll stick around
for a bit?

10:18.313 --> 10:20.271
Yeah, I'll get
my lava lamp warmed up,

10:20.315 --> 10:22.012
we can take
our shirts off.
Oh.

10:22.056 --> 10:23.753
